<section class="py-5 text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white;">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead mb-0">Your privacy is important to us. This policy is designed to help you understand what information we collect and how we use it.</p>
